ComicInfo.Title: A Walk on the Wild Side!
ComicInfo.Summary: A Walk on the Wild Side!: A mysterious group has freed Stilt-Man from prison and send him to steal a mysterious package for them. Thor stops Stilt-Man but then realizes that Blastaar is also working for the same group.
